#=============================================================================
# SpeedChange Mod Configuration
# 速度切换模组配置文件
#=============================================================================
#
# This file is an EXAMPLE reference showing all available config options.
# The actual config file is auto-generated by NeoForge at:
#   config/speed_change-common.toml
#
# 此文件为配置参考示例。实际配置文件由 NeoForge 自动生成于：
#   config/speed_change-common.toml
#
# To customize, edit the auto-generated file while the game is NOT running.
# 请在游戏未运行时编辑自动生成的文件。
